101 POLICY IMMRULES~
Immortal Rules/Guidelines
-------------------------
 
We, as immortals, are here to insure that our world runs with a minimal amount
  of distress and anarchy. To those ends here is a list of _Do's_and_Dont's_.
 
    Do's                                                       Dont's
==============================================================================
