1 PKILL PK~
PK -> Pkill -> Player Killing

Rules for PKILL  (10/14/97)

[1] Multi-killing of a player is illegal.  Multi-killing is defined
   as killing of the same character within 1 min real time by ANY other 
   character, or by killing of the same character within 10 min real time
   by the same killer.
	ex:
	   ILLEGAL->
	     Joe kills Frank.  Joe kills Frank again only 7 min
	     real time later.
	     Joe kills Frank.  Jim kills Franks only 10 sec. real
